&lt;li&gt;Arranging and conducting initial Executive and CxO discussions and positioning meetings – build strong relationships based on deep understanding of their priorities and goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing revenue growth plans with the marketing and channel teams that will exceed annual goal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales process management and opportunity closure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing account management to ensure a high level of customer satisfaction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
