&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years’ experience selling enterprise software.&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to understand the &quot;bigger picture&quot; and the business drivers around IT.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Account&amp;nbsp;management&amp;nbsp;and new business sales focus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate track record of achieving sales targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Defined sales process &amp;amp; methodology to drive repeatable &amp;amp; predictable results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years’ experience working for or with Federal focused Value-Added Resellers and/or System Integrators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ideally you will Top Secret/SCI (Preferred).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
