&lt;p&gt;As Senior Enterprise&amp;nbsp;Account Director,&amp;nbsp;you’ll&amp;nbsp;propel Ivanti’s growth in the Iberia market by architecting revenue growth through channels and major account development in Spain and Portugal. This strategic role calls for customer base account management, channel-focused sales acumen, outstanding performance in cultivating new business, and the discipline to work independently as the sole representative in your market.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
