&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate seamlessly with the marketing team to execute innovative marketing plans, driving robust pipeline generation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
