&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive enterprise software sales experience, with a strong emphasis on channel partnerships.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven&amp;nbsp;track record&amp;nbsp;of major account development and exceeding revenue goals in the Spanish and Portuguese markets.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
