&lt;h3&gt;Why this role matters&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, your work will support Ivanti’s mission to enable smarter, more connected operations across the business. While you will be part of our HRIS Team under Business Applications, who help modernize and scale our HR technology ecosystem by ensuring seamless data flow across Workday, Greenhouse, payroll, and finance systems, you will have a focus on Payroll, Benefits and Compensation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your contributions will reduce manual work, improve data accuracy, and enable more proactive, automated processes across the employee lifecycle. Your impact will be tangible—strengthening system reliability, enhancing decision-making through better data, and enabling scalable HR operations. You’ll work cross-functionally in a highly collaborative environment where your expertise directly shapes how systems operate across Ivanti and you will play a critical role in enabling HRIS transformation and system optimization&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and maintain integrations across Workday, Greenhouse, and downstream HR, payroll, and finance systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage end-to-end integration lifecycle, including requirements, design, development, testing, deployment, and support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own critical data flows across recruiting, hiring, onboarding, and position management processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with HR, Talent Acquisition, Payroll, Finance, and IT to translate business needs into scalable technical solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor integration performance, troubleshoot issues, and perform root cause analysis to ensure system reliability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive automation and continuous improvement initiatives to reduce manual processes and improve data quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on HRIS transformation efforts, leveraging best practices, AI capabilities, and integration standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What you will bring&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Required:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of experience in Workday or HRIS integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong expertise with Workday integration tools (Studio, EIB, Core Connectors, APIs – REST/SOAP)&lt;/li&gt;
